In his long awaited first comedy special, Drew Hastings examines
everything from the complexity of the human condition to the
uncertainties of misguided love, to his earnest attempts at
farming. Insightful, deeply self-deprecating and extremely hilarious,
Drew has made a name for himself as a regular guest on The Bob & Tom
Radio Show and live in concert in venues all over the country. With
his biting wit, Drew tackles the absurdities and frustrations of the
world, leaving his fans anything but Irked & Miffed.
